(41, 12, 29, 5, 6, 4, 4, 'The Lord our God is one Lord:', 'Connection of the Shema', 'Both passages emphasize the oneness of God, as expressed in the phrase ''The Lord our God is one Lord.'' This connection highlights the continuity of this fundamental belief in both the Old and New Testaments.', 'quotation', 0.503, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
