(41, 12, 29, 48, 3, 20, 20, 'God is one', 'Unity of God in Scripture', 'Both passages emphasize the oneness of God. Mark 12:29 declares that ''The Lord our God is one Lord,'' while Galatians 3:20 states, ''God is one,'' reinforcing the theme of divine unity.', 'theme', 0.419, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
